From 7ad300211d0567244d16a7a3e2ff71ed190b8429 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: l0m0eby <luc.masalar@walmart.com>
Date: Tue, 15 Jul 2025 15:53:14 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Fix Rich markdown rendering in message system

- Improved QueueConsole to properly handle Rich objects like Markdown
- Enhanced message renderers to correctly display Rich content instead of object representations
- Updated messaging system to maintain Rich object rendering context
- Added comprehensive test coverage for TUI Rich object rendering
- Cleaned up debug test files that are no longer needed

Rich markdown messages from agent reasoning and other sources now render properly as formatted markdown instead of showing <rich.markdown.Markdown object> representations.
